title: Hip-Hop and Rap Jam
description:
Hip-Hop and Rap Jam is a real hip-hop and rap station for your improvisation. You can use it anywhere in the street jams or enjoying the headphones. Powerful Percussion, great hip-hop effects and crazy bass line will allow you to create your own hip-hop and rap song with your friends. Enjoy yourself, play with your friends in jams, create a street hip-hop. Hip-Hop and Rap is the freedom of expression. Excellence in the use of Hip-Hop and Rap Jam and you will always be a street hip-hop rhythm master!

-= Features =-
- Multi Touch supported.
- Sound samples with professional equipment.
- Best hip-hop and rap station on your device.
- High quality sound samples.
- Enjoy the music .
- Use in street music jams.
- Maximum volume.
- Implemented a dynamic volume, now sound more lively.
